name: Star Trek: Khan #1
description:
Star Trek: Khan - The Official Star Trek Comic Book chronicling the back story of John Harrison, Khan... the character played by Benedict Cumberbatch in JJ Abrams' Into Darkness...

This is Paul's first Official Star Trek artwork and this comic could well become a collectors item as this artists career grows...

Issue #1 of 5

Signed by Cover Artist Paul Shipper on the cover and inside on preview page for his cover art for Issue #2 

Only 50 Available!

Postage and Packing $6.00 Worldwide

name: The Mind of Tim Burton - Limited Edition Print
description:
This illustration was created for Tim Burton month at Planet-Pulp. 

The portrait of Tim Burton features characters from his films intertwined throughout his hair. Jack Skellington from Nightmare Before Christmas, Batman, Frankenweenie, Sleepy Hollow, Mars Attacks, the Mad Hatter from Alice in Wonderland and Beetlejuice...

Signed Limited Edition of 100 Prints

8.25 x 11" Giclée Print
308gsm Hahnemühle FineArt Photo Rag

Ships flat in card envelope
